title: Lost Realms  Legacy of the Sun Princess - New Hidden Object - We
description:
Lost Realms - Legacy of the Sun Princess, blue lizard games



Alexia is woman in need of answers. Her nights are wracked with dark visions of an ancient Incan 

empire, burning and ruined. She sets out with her best friend Nicole to Cuzco, Peru, in search of 

ancestral ruins, armed with little more than visions, and hope. Help Alexia search for clues of 

her connection to the ancient Incas, and solve the mystery that devastated an empire. Devious 

puzzles await, but Alexia can not rest until she uncovers the truth.

Exotic tropical scenes
Clever mini-games and puzzles
Uncover an ageless mystery

System Requirements:
OS: Windows XP/Vista
CPU: 600 Mhz
RAM: 128 MB
DirectX: 7.0

Thanx to TAC-CM
